metadata.name: Cloud Kingdom #1
metadata.description: Cloud Kingdom is a collection of adorable clouds on the Ethereum blockchain. Artist Itzel and founders ItsGuthix and Melatonin envision a family friendly brand that can be enjoyed across the metaverse and physical world. The Cloud Universe is our most ambitious goal. Ownership grants you membership in the community, DAO, and will serve as a ticket for exclusive access into the Cloud Universe.
